This folder contains the input data generated by pre_processing_v3.py. pre_processing_v3.py is based on pre_processing_v2.py, while I improved the method for encoding road density.
I trained and test/valid two models: Multilayer Perceptron and Linear Regression model, getting their performances on the training set and validation set.
However, my experiments are only based the data_time_features_normalized.csv, which is generating from new train.csv.

